headline: Interactive Brokers Group to Present at Goldman Sachs Financial Services Conference
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., December 04, 2024--Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (Nasdaq: IBKR) announces that its Chairman Thomas Peterffy will speak at the Goldman Sachs Financial Services Conference on Wednesday, December 11th at 10:00 a.m. ET.
